{"tid":729270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[技術性病假]英軍入8強 預計500萬國民今稱病","createTime":"2018-07-04T11:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T12:01:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0b6e78f9aafe44c2e38dd1c985e2e32c801a45","tid":729270,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=TR2XzQCHhxIwPlhvyXzKjgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=92cf5648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英格蘭周二殺入世界盃8強，估計英國時間周三將多達500萬人「生病」。<br />\n<br />\n三獅軍團相隔12後再入世界盃8強，舉國歡騰，根據英國啤酒和酒店總會估計，翌日將會超過500萬人「生病」，無法如期上班。<br />\n<br />\n據知，大部份球迷因興奮過度，飲酒太多，導致翌日宿醉，難以上班，當中有16%考慮稱之為「生病」，另有8%表示「很可能稱之為生病」。<br />\n<br />\n全英國約2380萬人觀看英格蘭淘汰哥倫比亞，7%表示一定會「生病」，寧取病假，故此接近520萬打工仔翌日不會上班，數字驚人。<br />\n<br />\n研究指「睇波後請假」已在英國習以為常，即使超過5成球迷選擇留在家中睇波，只有7%球迷會在酒吧睇波，5%選擇留在朋友家睇波。"},{"pid":"7e32cc703547e2d38465ff5434f0912d0eb3cc3c","tid":729270,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"香港&hellip;翻工啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"89089a78a0726538d9410f2b5ff94184dd1dd6eb","tid":729270,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"香港人要番工 睇波 不了"},{"pid":"f785778cd91c00f180a4b15c23a3fa6d06cb23e4","tid":729270,"uid":3223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"英國晚餐時間睇波都可以第日射波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港2am 睇住廢英妹下妹下妹到加時12碼 5點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1e38f05c36042b2448aa903dd452d21615a6ec","tid":729270,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"香港人唔洗睇波都會射波"},{"pid":"62936fa14e551c13c5ac43e48ee20d770c5bb047","tid":729270,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"CHing Sick Ball<i